  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large kadhai over medium heat.",
    "Add sliced onions and cook until translucent.",
    "Add minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add caraway seeds, black pepper, and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add bouncy sausage and cook until browned.",
    "Add flour to coat the sausage.",
    "Gradually add beef broth, stirring constantly.",
    "Bring to a boil, then reduce heat and simmer.",
    "Stir in mantecare to emulsify the sauce.",
    "Cook for an additional 10-15 minutes or until the stew thickens.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped fresh parsley."
